original: Engdahl, Folke, tandläkare, Norrköping, f. 19/4/13 i Kristinehamn av pastor Adolf E. o. Emma Nilsson. G. m. Margareta Nilsson. Barn: Harriet f. 45. — Stud:ex. i Karlstad 32, med. stud. v. Karol. inst., tandl :kand. 34, tandl. 36. Prakt, i Norrköp. sed. 37. Hobby: segling.
translated: Engdahl, Folke, dentist, Norrköping, born on April 19th, 1913 in Kristinehamn to pastor Adolf E. and Emma Nilsson. Married to Margareta Nilsson since an unknown year. Children: Harriet born in 1945. He passed his studentexamen in Karlstad in 1932, and studied medicine at Karolinska institutet. He completed his dental studies in 1934 and became a licensed dentist in 1936. He started his practice in Norrköping in 1937. His hobby is sailing.
